channel.title: Changing rates in Project16
channel.description: Alright, I've searched everywhere (MoparScape, RS-Server.net, Dodian, even RaGEZONE), but can't find a thing on changing the rates in Project16 v6. I've changed all the hitdiff's to times 4 instead of 20k so you get 4 xp instead of 20k, but I still level up extremely fast (Not as fast as before, but still pretty quick). Anyone have any idea on what to do?

item.title: Changing rates in Project16
item.dc:creator: @Takajin Takajin++
item.description:
@Takajin wrote:

I’ve found where you USUALLY change rates, but it’s set to 1…

EDIT: Just thought I’d post where it’s usually found in case you find something near it that I missed. Open client.java and search for

	private int woodcutting[] = {0,0,0,1,-1,2};

The fourth number in the sequence of numbers is the rate for that skill.
